title: 089: Super Bowl Champ Brendon Ayanbadejo
description: Sal, Adam & Justin interview 3 time Pro Bowler and Super Bowl Champ Brendon Ayanbadejo. This is no ordinary interview. You are not only going to learn how he went from the projects in Chicago to Super Bowl glory, but about marijuana, anabolic steroids, roller skates and bow ties.
